data.description: Updated home in wilton manors.  1mile to everything the drive has to offer, .5 to I95, 1 block to Mickel Park or Donn Eisel Park. New roof in 2018, all impact windows and doors (including sun porch) AC in 2021 and pool liner and filter.  New cabinets, appliances, concrete counters, fixtures, faucets, shower panels, basket weave marble tile in kitchen and baths. Original terrazzo floors through out.  Too many updates to list.  Must see to appreciate.
